data.description: Spacious century home nestled on nearly half an acre within the sought-after South Range school district. While it awaits your personal touch, you'll appreciate the generous living space, convenient first-floor laundry, newer windows, and metal roof. Outside, a substantial 64x32 outbuilding with concrete floors and electricity provides ample room for storage, hobbies, or potential business endeavors.
